
This sample code is referred from the link:
http://blog.codinglabs.org/articles/intro-of-nginx-module-development.html

1. Build the static module in the nginx source code
1)./configure --prefix=/usr/local/nginx --add-module=/Users/rovin/Documents/media/nginx-echo-module
2)make
3)sudo make install

2. Build the dynamic module in the nginx source code
1)./configure --prefix=/usr/local/nginx --add-dynamic-module=/Users/rovin/Documents/media/nginx-echo-module
2)make
3)sudo make install

3. Modify the nginx conf file
    sudo vi /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf
    
4. Start the nginx
    sudo /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx
    
5. Stop the nginx
    sudo /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx -s stop


